Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the moe is gone from Akiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Tora no Ana? The Animate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mandarake? The Gamers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would those be in Akiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to Nakano to get my doujinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you work part-time at May Queen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May Queen Nyan Nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feyris was the one who asked \Nto bring moe culture to Akiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She sent a D-mail, preventing that from ever happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With just one message,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the whole town changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:26.93,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Theory Homeostasis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that \NMay Queen used to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May Queen? That a potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.61,0:02:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During summer, I prefer noodles to potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't a potato...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If May Queen never existed, \Nthen how did we meet Feyris?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's thanks to potato ramen that we met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day of the Rai-Net Tournament in Ikebukuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got sick from the potato ramen I had for lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I withdrew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii and you entered as a pair,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you went up against Feyris-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You totally lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Mayushii and Feyris-tan became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look, Ruka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought this cosplayer \Nphoto book yesterday, in Nakano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The past changed, but our relationships haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have lots of time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on your hands, this Obon, Lab Member Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's Sedona from {\i1}Blood Tune{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really detailed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a swimsuit version, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have those proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:03:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flat is justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not take all the lab members,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kurisu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wears their school swimsuits, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going swimming with a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well... I mean, if it's just the girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not be honest, Christina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone to see the mole on your rear,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mole!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's just the girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Rukako can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Rukako's actually a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you're a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you call a girl a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:05:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii doesn't like it \Nwhen you say stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that really mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Urushibara-san. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I apologize? It's true—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you think of me, Okabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, Rukako! You're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you keep that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Right here, you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone! There's nothing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-san, stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako, you're a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saying that this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit of torture...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Torture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Makise Kurisu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.94,0:06:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I fixed the misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She made me sit on my knees for an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean, I was tortured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That isn't torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost sound like you've been tortured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect day for cycling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go for a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you call cycling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to Tokyo to find my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he disappear or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even remember his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know he's in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my only clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A badge he used to own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't just kill time at \Na part-time job, should you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some stuff going on, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad might show up tomorrow, \Nat a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I miss that, I'll have to leave this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somewhere I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was always planning on \Ngiving up if I couldn't meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're uneasy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But too bad, part-time soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your luck ran out, the minute
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you spoke to the great \NMad Scientist, Hououin Kyouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now Lab Member 008!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be our guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may think me cruel if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no escape for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.42,0:08:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send a D-mail to your father, before he leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him not to leave his daughter behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good person, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a bit better now, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you see him tomorrow or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come by the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use your sentimentality
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for an experiment with the D-mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a mad scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now explain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.14,0:09:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the parameters of Operation Eldhrímnir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More Norse myths?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the part-time warrior meets her father,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll hold a celebration...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A last supper in Tokyo, for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if she doesn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will try to cheer her up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then send a D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's meeting his online friends tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he said he can't join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've taken steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:47.10,CellphoneR,,0000,0000,0000,,To: Daru \NSubject: Now is the time to choose \N\NFeyris's cooking or your meeting. \NWhich will you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent this message.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris's cooking or your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will you choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Feyris-chan can't come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris has never met the part-time warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Daru has a duty to \Nparticipate in this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I've never met this Suzuha-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you all shopping for the banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will follow the part-time warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and report in on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the father and daughter \Nhave their time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come shopping with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm following her—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me what to do, assistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to sit on your knees again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, for three hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then! Let's get things ready for the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.72,Cellphone,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think sweet curry is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or maybe spicy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Sure... Spicy, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, yeah! Suzu-san's a part-time warrior, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she's a warrior, she'll want spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um... Next, we need the meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beef is expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back there, you would've normally said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Organization's sabotage has \Nincreased the price of beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Operation Time Sale begun?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you use Norse mythology there, \Nnot "time sale."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Organization's sabotage has \Ncaused unexpected expenses
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Operation Audhumbla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm requesting additional funds for the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first star!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Venus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you got really sick, with a high fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The world was panicking \Nover the Y2K problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii was really scared you would die then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I prayed to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, there was a falling star.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to the falling star,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't die, Okarin!" three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.90,0:12:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the next day, you got better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the choice of Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I survived back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, remember what you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you got sick and collapsed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everything I saw began to flow together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suddenly, I shook and couldn't stand up."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked just like that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in Feyris-chan's condominium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That feeling I had when I got that fever
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was just like the feeling I get \Nwhen I move world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I attained my magic eye, Reading Steiner,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}at that moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's the smell of Kurisu-san's apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want Mayushii to help, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you boil an egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Can I use the microwave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put drop a raw egg in, it will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you chop up the mushrooms, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need mushrooms \Nor boiled eggs for apple pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the salad, to go with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think a boiled egg and mushroom salad \Nreally goes with apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop chopping up mushrooms over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've released the seals \Nthat bound a dark god.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't contact you within the hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell my parents that I loved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-san, do you have a rice cooker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Feyris-tan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Feyris-tan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida, you've been deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris-san said she couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I get a chance, I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really looking forward to my \Ntime machine forum meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time machine forum?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's with a sci-fi message board I frequent a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A professional author was supposed to go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an interestingly shaped mess kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a mess kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Future Gadget #4, The Moad Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A claymore mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made to look like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a super-instant humidifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Okabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, don't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, couldn't we use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vacuum cleaner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Future Gadget #3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or #2?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#5!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once Again I've Connected Something Useless
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Goemon."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it so you can use a \Nvacuum cleaner's output to warm a dryer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you use that, you need to turn off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,any other appliances, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll trigger the breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the flashlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Miss Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a daikon radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, where's the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you walk around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The breaker's in the front hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lab I worked at in America had some of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the best people from around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they all had really big heads,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it was a really hostile place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to them, your lab is really childish,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's a fun place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not praising you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just kinda thinking that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess maybe I simply wanted friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think of you as a companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I was your dear companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That made me really happy, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm trying to rethink my opinion of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she met her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they're finally spending time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to come to the lab, either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're aborting the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.93,CellphoneL,,0000,0000,0000,,From: Part-Time Warrior \NSubject: I'm sorry \N\NGoodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she plan to leave this city, by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Hououin Kyouma, will not allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I send a D-mail, telling myself to follow her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no matter what, this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it right for me to use the D-mail
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to change the past any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're a good person, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel a bit better now, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am the great Mad Scientist, Hououin Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I to fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not give in to your assistant's threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.10,CellphoneR,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not give in to your assistant's threats. \NFollow Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.27,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow Suzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, part-time warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slacking off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, we were all up really late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had a last supper for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you could be our guinea pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the experiment never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know my dad's phone's address.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did I catch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're underage. You shouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was heading back from the \Ntime machine forum meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time machine forum?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where your dad was supposed to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my dad's calling himself Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,John Titor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not John... Barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barrel Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you take a video of it on your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had fun last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been more fun \Nwithout Makise Kurisu, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her apple pie was man-killingly horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Urushibara Ruka's curry was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your lab's kinda nice, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's friends, and you \Nalways seem to have fun.
